{"tid":931662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女優招手貓系男 豪乳轟炸龍山寺","createTime":"2018-12-07T07:41:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T08:58:29.000Z","uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c9ee305cc855061630dd63825cfb5b5e8e7b9d0b","tid":931662,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T07:41:38.000Z","msg":"31歲日本「史上最強胴體」AV女優JULIA擁有J罩杯傲人上圍，她最近擔任《JKF》雜誌12月號封面女郎，之前特別走訪獨具台灣風味的小旅館，與台北龍山寺等景點拍照，大秀性感風情。<br />\n<br />\n出道8年的JULIA，先後拍過逾1000部AV，床戰經驗豐富，她也積極學中文，以中文在微博、IG上PO文，拉近與華語圈粉絲的距離。她至今仍是單身，透露以往欣賞積極上進、對她百依百順的男生，後來覺得這樣的男生缺乏個性，她說：「我現在欣賞令人捉摸不定，個性神祕的貓系男子，這樣的男生比較新鮮有趣。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1oVUugQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1oVUugQ.png&h=5c38c90c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ae59628c058c0dceacb47c3b9ea4067d01304a0","tid":931662,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T07:44:32.000Z","msg":"咁佢要試下認識我"},{"pid":"368ee30524218e405d41ee18eb19aa5822fbea47","tid":931662,"uid":12208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T07:45:31.000Z","msg":"喵"},{"pid":"e8d01f581ff9c6a91bd99e03fdc7453ea795b45c","tid":931662,"uid":89514,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T07:47:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88105d33432772959580956e69499adf78951bd8","tid":931662,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T07:50:40.000Z","msg":"愈嚟愈似隻馬"},{"pid":"0fb8cca93e025fe70559fc8b35abeda1d7600995","tid":931662,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c023ef9e1d2113de775e91b3be54eeb598192cea","tid":931662,"uid":86316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:38:36.000Z","msg":"好撚樣衰"},{"pid":"15a0e47a575a8b74f1669c4645b2fc8261b48794","tid":931662,"uid":59602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r